snippet.title: Starship Troopers: Terran Command - Raising Hell | Announcement teaser trailer
snippet.description:
FEDNET BREAKING NEWS: Mobilize Troopers, we have DLC coming in hot. Brace yourselves for a firestorm of action as Starship Trooper: Terran Command proudly announces its new DLC, "Raising Hell". Gehenna, an infernal hellscape, is overrun by the savage Arachnid horde. But fear not, for the Mobile Infantry is en route to give the Bugs the boot. Get ready to embark on a perilous journey, defending Vilon Station and humanity itself. Service guarantees citizenship, Troopers. Would you like to know more?

🎮 Wishlist it on Steam ➡️ https://bit.ly/4722G6L
💬 Join the Discord Server ➡️ https://discord.gg/gAwt99fpmP
🦎 More info on Slitherine ➡️ https://bit.ly/3QxEkui
